## ğŸ§  Summary

| Component       | Role                                      |
|----------------|-------------------------------------------|
| API Gateway     | Entry point, routing, security, filters   |
| Eureka          | Service registry for discovery            |
| Microservices   | Business logic, registered with Eureka    |

